    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has some visible scratches, minor dings, and the clear coat is starting to fade in a few spots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, although it will eventually need attention for a minor oil seep and some suspension bushings that are beginning to creak. It's a solid, functional car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
