      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I'm parting with my car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, well-loved, and ready for its next adventure! It runs like a dream and has been maintained with a lot of care. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a quality vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
